  "prompt": "Which are the least expensive and still good 3D/4D cinema theaters in Delhi NCR?",
  "response": "While I don't have access to real-time pricing or specific current offers, I can provide some general guidance on finding affordable 3D/4D cinema theaters in the Delhi NCR region. Here are some popular chains and suggestions that are generally considered to be budget-friendly and provide a good cinema experience:\n\n1. **PVR Cinemas**: While PVR can be on the pricier side, they offer various locations and sometimes have discounts or special pricing for morning shows. Check their websites for specific offers.\n\n2. **INOX**: Similar to PVR, INOX often has promotional offers, especially for weekdays or early bird screenings. They also have a good selection of 3D/4D films.\n\n3. **Cinepolis**: Known for offering competitive prices, particularly during off-peak times. They also have multiple offerings for 3D/4D movies.\n\n4. **Wadhawan Multiplex (also known as Wave Cinemas)**: Known for affordable pricing, they sometimes provide good deals on movie tickets and may have promotions for 3D films.\n\n5. **Fun Cinemas**: Often has lower price points compared to major chains and offers 3D showings.\n\nTo find the most affordable showtimes, consider:\n\n- **Online Booking**: Check websites or apps like BookMyShow for discounts or combo offers.\n- **Weekday Shows**: Tickets are often cheaper during weekdays as opposed to weekends.\n- **Promotional Days**: Many cinemas have specific days when tickets are discounted.\n- **Student Discounts**: If you\u2019re a student, some theaters offer student discounts upon showing valid ID.\n\nIt\u2019s always a good idea to look up reviews and current pricing online before making a decision.",
